query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android-lifecycle',
'argparse',
'azure-service-fabric',
'dotnetopenauth',
'expo',
'hashcode',
'impersonation',
'interrupt',
'laravel-blade',
'rdlc',
'rollback',
'sidekiq',
'stdin')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Autobiographer',
'Editor',
'Excavator',
'Informed',
'Necromancer',
'Notable Question',
'Peer Pressure',
'Popular Question',
'Supporter',
'Teacher',
'Tumbleweed');
